videos.headline: Kentucky gets loose for a 55-yard  TD run
videos.description: Kentucky RB Asim Rose runs for a 55-yard touchdown against Central Michigan.

videos.headline: Central Michigan turns Kentucky fumble into TD
videos.description: Central Michigan CB Devonni Reed recovers and returns a Kentucky fumble for a 20-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kentucky RB leaps through defenders for a 52-yard score
videos.description: Kentucky RB Benny Snell Jr. hurdles Central Michigan defenders for a long run.

videos.headline: Kentucky takes the lead right before the half
videos.description: Kentucky QB Gunnar Hoak throws a 24-yard strike to WR David Bouvier to end the first half.

videos.headline: Kentucky RB breaks tackles for 11-yard TD
videos.description: Kentucky RB Benny Snell Jr. breaks a tackle to get into the end zone for an 11-yard touchdown to put the Wildcats up  by a possession over Central Michigan.
